This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) because it deals with the recognition of noun phrases, which is a common task in NLP. The use of machine learning algorithms and different representations of the data also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of voting techniques for combining the results could suggest that it belongs to the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the potential use of image data for noun phrase recognition could also suggest that it belongs to the sub-category of Computer Vision (cs.CV).
